data.description: Welcome to this enchanting three bedroom, one and a half bath Century Colonial Home that seamlessly blends historic charm with eclectic flair! Nestled in the highly sought-after Lakewood neighborhood, this residence is a true gem that boasts character and modern convenience. Immerse yourself in the timeless beauty of hardwood floors that grace every room, adding an extra touch of warmth and elegance to this charming home. The generous living spaces are perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The living room features a cozy fireplace, ideal for chilly evenings, while the dining room boasts a large eat-at bar, creating a casual and inviting space that is seamlessly open to the kitchen. An additional sunroom bathed in natural light offers the perfect space for a studio or home office. With plenty of windows and a tranquil atmosphere, this room provides an inspiring setting for creativity or productive remote work. Step outside to a private backyard oasis!! This property features a beautiful outdoor living space with mature landscaping that blooms with hundreds of different flowers, fruits, and vegetables every year!  Imagine enjoying the ever-changing colors and scents that surround your home, creating a delightful and serene environment. The basement has been completely waterproofed with a transferrable lifetime warranty. Enjoy the convenience of being within close proximity to a variety of restaurants, shops, parks, and schools. Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful home your own!
